	appliesTo (optional): A comma-separated list of classes for which the attribute can
				      be used, e.g. "MyCustomItem".
	default (optional): The default-value of the attribute.
	values (optional): All allowed values in a comma-separated list.
	id (optional): The (short) ID of this attribute, use IDs between 1000 and 9999 for custom attributes. The ID is required for
